name: AUSTRALIAN INTERNATIONAL AVIATION COLLEGE PTY LTD
about: Australian International Aviation College (AIAC) is a premier flight training institution dedicated to producing highly skilled airline pilots, flight instructors, and corporate pilots. Approved by the Australian Civil Aviation Safety Authority (CASA), AIAC offers comprehensive training programs that meet international standards. Our graduates have successfully secured positions with major airlines such as Qantas and Cathay Pacific, thanks to our strong network of global partners and industry specialists. With a focus on quality training and career success, AIAC provides a supportive and professional environment, ensuring students are well-equipped for a bright future in aviation. Our commitment to excellence and student success makes AIAC a leading choice for aspiring pilots.
